
        INSERT INTO "Attributes" ("NameTranslate", "Name", "Type") 
        SELECT '2', '2', 'Количество конфорок'
        WHERE NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "Attributes" WHERE "Name" = '2' AND "Type" = 'Количество конфорок'
        );

        INSERT INTO "AttributeCategory" ("AttributeID", "CategoryID") 
        SELECT a."ID", c."ID" FROM "Attributes" a, "Categories" c 
        WHERE a."Name" = '2' AND a."Type" = 'Количество конфорок' 
        AND c."Name" = 'builtin'
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "AttributeCategory" WHERE "AttributeID" = a."ID" AND "CategoryID" = c."ID"
        );

        INSERT INTO "Attributes" ("NameTranslate", "Name", "Type") 
        SELECT 'индукционные', 'индукционные', 'Тип конфорок'
        WHERE NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "Attributes" WHERE "Name" = 'индукционные' AND "Type" = 'Тип конфорок'
        );

        INSERT INTO "AttributeCategory" ("AttributeID", "CategoryID") 
        SELECT a."ID", c."ID" FROM "Attributes" a, "Categories" c 
        WHERE a."Name" = 'индукционные' AND a."Type" = 'Тип конфорок' 
        AND c."Name" = 'builtin'
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "AttributeCategory" WHERE "AttributeID" = a."ID" AND "CategoryID" = c."ID"
        );

        AND c."Name" = 'builtin'
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "AttributeCategory" WHERE "AttributeID" = a."ID" AND "CategoryID" = c."ID"
        );

        WHERE a."Name" = 'автоматический/ механический' AND a."Type" = 'Электроподжиг конфорок' 
        AND c."Name" = 'builtin'
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "AttributeCategory" WHERE "AttributeID" = a."ID" AND "CategoryID" = c."ID"
        );

        AND c."Name" = 'builtin'
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "AttributeCategory" WHERE "AttributeID" = a."ID" AND "CategoryID" = c."ID"
        );

        AND c."Name" = 'builtin'
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "AttributeCategory" WHERE "AttributeID" = a."ID" AND "CategoryID" = c."ID"
        );

        AND c."Name" = 'builtin'
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "AttributeCategory" WHERE "AttributeID" = a."ID" AND "CategoryID" = c."ID"
        );

        AND c."Name" = 'builtin'
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "AttributeCategory" WHERE "AttributeID" = a."ID" AND "CategoryID" = c."ID"
        );

        WHERE a."Name" = '41' AND a."Type" = 'Объем духовки' 
        AND c."Name" = 'builtin'
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "AttributeCategory" WHERE "AttributeID" = a."ID" AND "CategoryID" = c."ID"
        );

        AND c."Name" = 'builtin'
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "AttributeCategory" WHERE "AttributeID" = a."ID" AND "CategoryID" = c."ID"
        );

        WHERE a."Name" = 'ТЭН (верхний/нижний)' AND a."Type" = 'Тип гриля' 
        AND c."Name" = 'builtin'
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "AttributeCategory" WHERE "AttributeID" = a."ID" AND "CategoryID" = c."ID"
        );

        AND c."Name" = 'builtin'
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "AttributeCategory" WHERE "AttributeID" = a."ID" AND "CategoryID" = c."ID"
        );

        AND c."Name" = 'builtin'
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "AttributeCategory" WHERE "AttributeID" = a."ID" AND "CategoryID" = c."ID"
        );

        );

        AND c."Name" = 'builtin'
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "AttributeCategory" WHERE "AttributeID" = a."ID" AND "CategoryID" = c."ID"
        );

        AND c."Name" = 'builtin'
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "AttributeCategory" WHERE "AttributeID" = a."ID" AND "CategoryID" = c."ID"
        );

        WHERE a."Name" = 'ТЭН (верхний/нижний)' AND a."Type" = 'Тип гриля' 
        AND c."Name" = 'builtin'
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "AttributeCategory" WHERE "AttributeID" = a."ID" AND "CategoryID" = c."ID"
        );


        INSERT INTO "Attributes" ("NameTranslate", "Name", "Type") 
        SELECT '85*50*58.5 см', '85*50*58.5 см', 'Габаритные размеры (В*Ш*Г)'
        WHERE NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "Attributes" WHERE "Name" = '85*50*58.5 см' AND "Type" = 'Габаритные размеры (В*Ш*Г)'
        );

        INSERT INTO "AttributeCategory" ("AttributeID", "CategoryID") 
        SELECT a."ID", c."ID" FROM "Attributes" a, "Categories" c 
        WHERE a."Name" = '85*50*58.5 см' AND a."Type" = 'Габаритные размеры (В*Ш*Г)' 
        AND c."Name" = 'builtin'
        AND NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM "AttributeCategory" WHERE "AttributeID" = a."ID" AND "CategoryID" = c."ID"
        );
